<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Altron lifts half yr share, no div.</title>
<headline>Altron lifts half yr share, no div.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1996-10-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Half year ended August 31 1996</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)</p>
<p>Shr:</p>
<p>    - headline (cts)	28.0     vs   27.8</p>
<p>    - attributable (cts)  22.6     vs   15.4</p>
<p>    Attrib income	   43.67    vs   29.63</p>
<p>    Pre-tax		  154.21    vs   88.85</p>
<p>    Tax			 64.27    vs   50.45</p>
<p>    Interest received     12.38    vs    1.80 paid</p>
<p>    Turnover	     2,352.89    vs 2,267.72</p>
<p>    Exceptional items   29.68 loss vs 59.66 loss</p>
<p>Full name: Allied Electronics Corp Ltd (electronics)</p>
<p>NOTE - The company said that restructuring and rationalisation programmes initiated during the previous financial year made a positive contribution to the significant improvement in operating performance.</p>
<p>This process of continued profit enhancement would be maintained with a substantial improvement in results for the full year.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
